widgets.css:
JS{
var css=''

if(@{this} === 0) css =
' .mute {background: black; '
+ ' height: 55px; width: 40px; '
+ ' border-radius:10px; } '

if(@{this}==1) css =
' .mute {background: orange; '
+ ' height: 55px; width: 40px; '
+ ' border-radius:10px; '
+ ' animation: rapide 250ms infinite alternate;} '
+ ' @keyframes rapide '
+ ' { 0% { transform: scale(.2,.2); }  100% { transform: scale(1,1); } } ' 

return css
}
